I needed a script that would check my ISP IP and if it has changed send me an e-mail.

The original idea was taken from:
http://www.macosxhints.com/article.php?story=2004102508055243

The service I am using to check my IP: http://checkip.dyndns.org
The modules I am using to send email:
Email::Send
Email::Send::Gmail
Email::Simple::Creator

These are possible dependencies but try running script without them
sudo apt-get install libcrypt-ssleay-perl
sudo apt-get install libio-socket-ssl-perl
sudo apt-get install libauthen-sasl-perl
sudo apt-get install libnet-smtp-ssl-perl
